Regional news coverage of the Tamworth area is provided on all three main commercial networks.
Canberra-based Prime7 produces and airs a 30-minute local news program for the Tamworth area at 6:00 pm.
Newcastle-based NBN Television airs news, sport and weather opt-outs for the area within its hour-long 6:00 pm bulletin, while Southern Cross Ten airs short local news updates throughout the day.
Subscription television services are provided by Austar.
